document.text: The current specifications for glass mat and slit glass mat can be made more accurate and complete with the following changes:

Delete C- glass from item description Change bobbins per stack to 47 from 45. Add outside diameter specs of 30.0, 26.0 - 31.0 inches.
Change the current MSS specifications as outlined above.
